    "plan_content": "## Plan Summary\n\n**Bug:** Off-by-one error in `src/utils.ts`, line 7.\n\n**Root Cause:** The loop condition `i < items.length - 1` stops one index short, so the last element is always skipped.\n\n**Fix:** One-character change — remove the `- 1`:\n```typescript\n// Before (buggy)\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length - 1; i++) {\n\n// After (fixed)\nfor (let i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {\n```\n\n**Impact:** 3 of 4 `processItems` tests currently fail. After the fix, all 6 tests should pass. The `sum` function is unaffected (it correctly uses `for...of`).",
